they feel that what's being done now is contrary to 
the best interests of Austin? Oh, I think there's a

25:13.683 --> 25:18.910
lot of romanticism attached with when we were 
young. I think that people remember Austin from

25:20.813 --> 25:27.542
the time they went to the University of Texas here 
and what a good time it was. Indeed. And I think a lot

25:28.536 --> 25:33.540
of us look back at our undergraduate days and say, 
