25:33.640 --> 25:38.764
ways, I was young, healthy, and I really didn't 
realize all of the limitations I really have. Did

25:39.325 --> 25:40.426
you go to UT, also? No. I was wondering. No. But I 
appreciated the social life at Texas. Matter of

25:48.713 --> 25:52.496
fact, my junior year, I spent as much time over here 
