30:48.008 --> 30:54.715
for Austin and its residents than, say, it was 
during the 50s and 60s. I would have taken a real

30:55.606 --> 31:00.712
financial beating to try to live here in the 50s or 
60s, I think, as compared to today. Not that I'm

